{"tid":1350793,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"消防水龍頭用法","createTime":"2019-07-22T13:45:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T16:23:03.000Z","uid":92397,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"deab54fc896bb1d45e44ad52692a7b835b681f3c","tid":1350793,"uid":92397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:45:40.000Z","msg":"見到琴日係元朗有人用消防龍頭黎自保<br />\n諗法係幾好 但用法就未必正確<br />\n<br />\n消防水龍頭係正常既情況下<br />\n未係處於一個standby既狀態<br />\n水缸只有一定既壓力 <br />\n用得越耐水壓就會越低 <br />\n<br />\n因為水龍頭只係將水缸儲落既水放出黎 <br />\n但係只要我地將break glass 打爆<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cT5mPsy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcT5mPsy.png&h=c543221b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n水泵就會active 水壓就升到baba聲<br />\n消防亦會馬上出動 <br />\n<br />\n水泵係唔會自動停既 冇任何sensor <br />\n只有消防到場或相關人士落到水泵防 <br />\n手動打製先會停 <br />\n唔好睇少行緊泵既水壓 <br />\n平時試水壓既時候 <br />\n起馬要三人以上踩實個水龍頭 <br />\n要防止敵人進攻絕對有用 <br />\n<br />\n另外如果消防泵行左太耐都未有人落到水泵防打掣 <br />\nD水喉好易會爆同穿架 <br />\n所以大家唔好亂玩呀同阻住人打製呀"},{"pid":"ac052fbd55057b8ab1a6cf17b5b0aeaab194436c","tid":1350793,"uid":167792,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:47:49.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"efece1cfb99de59c56b5cfcfde7f3201c3b7f155","tid":1350793,"uid":159236,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:47:49.000Z","msg":"唔怪得救火咁大力，學到嘢"},{"pid":"f3b8f3aadad551c4b8524e76fa917ac7b92aaafe","tid":1350793,"uid":449,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:52:42.000Z","msg":"good"},{"pid":"840c75c235bc387552f2150c7fe6583046a2a8f5","tid":1350793,"uid":226471,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:54:05.000Z","msg":"長知識了"},{"pid":"13135fa41a0780c57438dcb493d1ff28b1d160e7","tid":1350793,"uid":258465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:03:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65f15722134bc087a5c7e4b43e8108b86b4c68e4","tid":1350793,"uid":18739,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T14:29:56.000Z","msg":"總之有事即刻break glass！消防都要出車幫拖！"},{"pid":"96046c772a2e45e8af33ca0021f3c13f560924da","tid":1350793,"uid":92397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:03:53.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"f66bcc374d340ee62cac97547fb97644301ca767","tid":1350793,"uid":92479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:31:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cafcd6f0e3b60159b13175e3345fcd4a1290181","tid":1350793,"uid":263161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:47:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fe0b6e3a99b0b0d76988034c541e42c062761a3a","tid":1350793,"uid":91527,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:23:03.000Z","msg":"正確叫法係消防喉轆  (因為真係個大轆)<br />\n點樣用其實個轆附近都有塊牌仔說明<br />\n<br />\np.s. 打爆個breakglass  會變成火警狀態<br />\n除左會直接call到消防之外<br />\n正常情況下所有對街外既逃生出口/大門<br />\n即使有鎖住都會全部自動解開鎖 <br />\n<br />\n所以真係千祈唔好亂用"}]}